{"tid":1022409,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都係好鍾意玩超現實既game","createTime":"2019-02-15T04:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T05:52:45.000Z","uid":200328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c55426d290572f53f8fd339dcac1cd93167f7e35","tid":1022409,"uid":200328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:07:11.000Z","msg":"個人由細個玩PS開始一路都係鍾意啲超現實既game多<br />\n魔幻, 科幻, 玄幻都可以, 就係好唔鍾意玩啲偏現實既game<br />\n發現依家3A大作品質就高左好多啦, 但好多都越黎越現實, 大家有冇啲超現實啲既大作推薦下?<br />\n<br />\n個人都唔鍾意from software果啲, 因為用親啲主角都廢到現實普通人咁, 但就走去打啲超現實boss<br />\n唔係難度既問題, 即係仁王咁我都幾鍾意(只講第一週目, 都唔算易啦), 唔係講品質, 純粹講緊個題材仁王成件事對我黎講係舒服啲<br />\n<br />\n又或者係任天堂, 鍾意任天堂其中一個原因係任天堂基本上都係超現實作品, 有種童心既超現實係入面, 同時係重視遊戲性遠高於現實性<br />\n相反既例子我會話RDR2係重視現實性遠高於遊戲性既作品<br />\n<br />\n近期就期待緊隻Anthem, 科幻大作<br />\n大家又有冇啲超現實既大作推介?"},{"pid":"72aee67048be52ec73c14e21b2910917cce3772f","tid":1022409,"uid":44333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:23:57.000Z","msg":"媾女GAME"},{"pid":"bddd9eccec1ee491ee7ef568c502d67dbc9fc56f","tid":1022409,"uid":200328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72aee67048be52ec73c14e21b2910917cce3772f","tid":1022409,"uid":44333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:23:57.000Z","msg":"媾女GAME"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:36:07.000Z","msg":"唔係呢種超現實啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4ad9606982322773603c06e6b4f888f5a50a5f","tid":1022409,"uid":194012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bddd9eccec1ee491ee7ef568c502d67dbc9fc56f","tid":1022409,"uid":200328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72aee67048be52ec73c14e21b2910917cce3772f","tid":1022409,"uid":44333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:23:57.000Z","msg":"媾女GAME"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:36:07.000Z","msg":"唔係呢種